## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ivacaftor Kalydeco 2012** = first FDA CFTR potentiator. G551D (~4% CF 환자) — 첫 disease-modifying CFTR modulator. quantum-VQE 의 ATP-binding domain + ion-channel gating fit. CF 의 paradigm "modulator era" 시작.
2. **Trikafta/Kaftrio 2019** = first FDA F508del heterozygous (90% 환자 cover) — elexacaftor + tezacaftor + ivacaftor 삼중. 2020 6+ → 2021 6+ → 2022 12+ → 2023 2-5세 expansion. CF 평균 수명 2010 30대 → 2024 50+ 추정.
3. **vanzacaftor + tezacaftor + deutivacaftor 2024 Phase 3 SKYLINE** = next-gen 4-mod (Vertex VX-121/VX-561) — better F508del + once-daily + lower hepatotoxicity. 2025-26 expected FDA. quantum-VQE 의 corrector cooperative binding leverage.
4. **rare CFTR variant 4-5%** = Trikafta non-eligible — N1303K + R117H + 일부 stop codon + CFTR splice. n-of-1 ASO + ELX-02 read-through + CRISPR 가 candidate. 한국 K-CF 환자 100명 이하 — 식약처 rare framework.
5. **inhaled CFTR mRNA (VX-522 ARCT-032 + 4DMT 2024 Phase 1)** = non-modulator-eligible CF (modulator-naive variant + read-through fail) — aerosolized lipid mRNA. quantum-VQE 의 mRNA tertiary fold + airway 표적 fit.
6. **AAV CFTR airway gene therapy historical fail (1990s-2000s)** = 초기 면역 + 표적 부족 → 2024+ lenti + AAV next-gen capsid (Translate Bio + 4DMT) research. 양자-VQE 의 capsid 면역회피 + airway tropism 가 가능.
7. **Pseudomonas 만성** = TOBI 1997 + Cayston 2010 + colistin + ciprofloxacin inhaled — 만성 chronic suppression. 양자-VQE fit 한정 (small molecule 표적 X — antibiotic resistance + biofilm).
8. **NTM 만성 (ALIS amikacin liposomal 2018)** = refractory MAC — first FDA inhaled liposomal. CF + non-CF bronchiectasis 양쪽 적응. cross-pulmonology + cross-hai_nosocomial.
9. **PERT + 지용성 비타민 + zinc** = 만성 외분비 결핍 — Trikafta 후 영양 개선이 의외로 측정. cross-nutritional_pharmacology + cross-hepatology.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, CF rare variant + AAV + ASO 임상 의미 한정. 한국 K-CF 환자 100명 이하 = clinical-translation gap.

